the second ':' in the ::)

the first smile was about a young boy trying to find his footing in this world, embracing the good and the bad, the ups and the downs. the second smile is about him realizing that in order to keep sane in this ever fast moving world he needs to keep his inner child alive, the one that believed joy was the journey. 

he decides to set fourth in the storm with nothing but a smile and memories to keep him grounded ::)
